---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import AudioPlayer from "../components/AudioPlayer";
import RevealButton from "../components/landing/RevealButton";
---

<Layout title="Tu cerebro te engaña">
  <article class="flex flex-col mt-8 mb-8">
    <!-- Seccion de "Oh no!" -->
    <section class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-[15px] w-[85%] sm:w-[75%] mx-auto">
      <img
        src="/images/svg/landing/Oh_No.svg"
        alt="Texto que dice 'Oh no!'"
        class="object-contain
            w-[720px]
            col-span-8 row-span-2 place-self-center"
      />
      <img
        src="/images/svg/landing/Emoji_Sorprendido.svg"
        alt="Emoji sorprendido"
        class="object-contain
            w-[236.99px]
            col-span-4 row-span-2 col-start-9 place-self-end"
      />
      <p
        class="text-start
        sm:text-center
            text-3xl
            sm:text-5xl
            col-span-11 col-start-1
            sm:col-span-12 sm:col-start-1 w-full"
      >
        <span class="text-mediumbold"
          >Mi cerebro me engaña al leer en
          <span class="text-[#6610F2] text-bold">inglés</span>...</span
        >
      </p>
    </section>
    <!-- Seccion de "¿Cómo puedo aprender?" -->
    <section
      class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-[15px] w-[85%] sm:w-[75%] space-y-8 mx-auto mt-20 sm:mt-24"
    >
      <p
        class="text-center
            text-base
            sm:text-2xl
            col-span-12"
      >
        Para que puedas notar <span class="text-bold"
          >cómo tu cerebro te engaña al leer una palabra en
        </span><span class="text-[#6610F2] text-bold">inglés, </span>pon
        atención a los siguientes pares de palabras:
      </p>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col items-center
            col-span-6
            sm:col-span-2 sm:col-start-4"
      >
        <p class="text-[#6610F2] text-3xl sm:text-5xl text-extrabold">Fir</p>
        <AudioPlayer
          audio_path={"/audio/landing/Fir.mp3"}
          className="w-24 h-24 sm:w-20 sm:h-20"
          client:load
        />
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col items-center
            col-span-6 col-start-7
            sm:col-span-2 sm:col-start-8"
      >
        <p class="text-[#6610F2] text-3xl sm:text-5xl text-extrabold">Fur</p>
        <AudioPlayer
          audio_path={"/audio/landing/Fur.mp3"}
          className="w-24 h-24 sm:w-20 sm:h-20"
          client:load
        />
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col items-center
            col-span-6
            sm:col-span-2 sm:col-start-4"
      >
        <p class="text-[#6610F2] text-3xl sm:text-5xl text-extrabold">Chip</p>
        <AudioPlayer
          audio_path={"/audio/landing/Chip.mp3"}
          className="w-24 h-24 sm:w-20 sm:h-20"
          client:load
        />
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col items-center
            col-span-6 col-start-7
            sm:col-span-2 sm:col-start-8"
      >
        <p class="text-[#6610F2] text-3xl sm:text-5xl text-extrabold">Ship</p>
        <AudioPlayer
          audio_path={"/audio/landing/Ship.mp3"}
          className="w-24 h-24 sm:w-20 sm:h-20"
          client:load
        />
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col items-center
            col-span-6
            sm:col-span-2 sm:col-start-4"
      >
        <p class="text-[#6610F2] text-3xl sm:text-5xl text-extrabold">Hi</p>
        <AudioPlayer
          audio_path={"/audio/landing/Hi.mp3"}
          className="w-24 h-24 sm:w-20 sm:h-20"
          client:load
        />
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col items-center
            col-span-6 col-start-7
            sm:col-span-2 sm:col-start-8"
      >
        <p class="text-[#6610F2] text-3xl sm:text-5xl text-extrabold">High</p>
        <AudioPlayer
          audio_path={"/audio/landing/High.mp3"}
          className="w-24 h-24 sm:w-20 sm:h-20"
          client:load
        />
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col items-center
            col-span-6
            sm:col-span-2 sm:col-start-4"
      >
        <p class="text-[#6610F2] text-3xl sm:text-5xl text-extrabold">Boat</p>
        <AudioPlayer
          audio_path={"/audio/landing/Boat.mp3"}
          className="w-24 h-24 sm:w-20 sm:h-20"
          client:load
        />
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col items-center
            col-span-6 col-start-7
            sm:col-span-2 sm:col-start-8"
      >
        <p class="text-[#6610F2] text-3xl sm:text-5xl text-extrabold">Vote</p>
        <AudioPlayer
          audio_path={"/audio/landing/Vote.mp3"}
          className="w-24 h-24 sm:w-20 sm:h-20"
          client:load
        />
      </div>
      <img
        src="/images/svg/landing/Emoji_Pensando.svg"
        alt="Emoji pensando"
        class="object-contain
            min-w-[90px]
            col-span-6 col-start-4 place-self-center
            sm:w-[164px]
            sm:col-span-2 sm:row-span-4 sm:col-start-1 sm:row-start-2"
      />
    </section>
    <!-- Sección de comparación -->
    <section
      class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-[15px] w-[85%] sm:w-[75%] mx-auto mt-16 sm:mt-24"
    >
      <img
        src="/images/svg/global/Estrella.svg"
        alt="Estrella"
        class="object-contain
            w-[104px] col-start-1 col-span-3 max-sm:translate-y-32
            lg:col-start-1 lg:col-span-2 place-self-center"
      />
      <p
        class="text-center
            text-base
            sm:text-2xl
            col-span-10 col-start-2 max-sm:w-[90%] max-sm:mx-auto
            lg:col-span-8 lg:col-start-3 my-auto"
      >
        De los cuatro pares de palabras que leíste, <span class="text-bold"
          >¿cuáles son <span class="text-[#6610F2]">iguales</span> y cuáles son <span
            class="text-[#6610F2]">diferentes</span
          >?</span
        >
      </p>
      <img
        src="/images/svg/global/Estrella.svg"
        alt="Estrella"
        class="object-contain
            w-[104px] col-span-3 col-start-10 max-sm:-translate-y-12
            lg:col-span-2 lg:col-start-11 place-self-center"
      />
      <div
        class="flex flex-col items-center mt-20 sm:mt-24
            col-span-1 col-start-2 lg:col-span-3 lg:col-start-1"
      >
        <p class="text-[#6610F2] text-2xl sm:text-5xl text-extrabold">Fir</p>
        <AudioPlayer
          audio_path={"/audio/landing/Fir.mp3"}
          className="w-20 h-20 sm:w-20 sm:h-20"
          client:load
        />
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col items-center mt-20 sm:mt-24
            col-start-4 col-span-1 lg:col-span-3 lg:col-start-4"
      >
        <p class="text-[#6610F2] text-2xl sm:text-5xl text-extrabold">Fur</p>
        <AudioPlayer
          audio_path={"/audio/landing/Fur.mp3"}
          className="w-20 h-20 sm:w-20 sm:h-20"
          client:load
        />
      </div>
      <img
        src="/images/svg/landing/Flecha_Derecha.svg"
        alt="Flecha Derecha"
        class="object-contain mt-8 mx-auto
            col-start-5 col-span-3 place-self-center
            sm:w-[165px]
            sm:col-span-2 sm:col-start-7 sm:place-self-center"
      />
      <div
        class="col-start-8 col-span-5 lg:col-start-9 lg:col-span-4 sm:col-start-10 sm:col-span-3 m-auto"
      >
        <RevealButton word={"Iguales"} client:load />
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col items-center mt-8 sm:mt-24
            col-span-3 col-start-1"
      >
        <p class="text-[#6610F2] text-2xl sm:text-5xl text-extrabold">Chip</p>
        <AudioPlayer
          audio_path={"/audio/landing/Chip.mp3"}
          className="w-24 h-24 sm:w-20 sm:h-20"
          client:load
        />
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col items-center mt-8 sm:mt-24
            col-span-3 col-start-4"
      >
        <p class="text-[#6610F2] text-2xl sm:text-5xl text-extrabold">Ship</p>
        <AudioPlayer
          audio_path={"/audio/landing/Ship.mp3"}
          className="w-24 h-24 sm:w-20 sm:h-20"
          client:load
        />
      </div>
      <img
        src="/images/svg/landing/Flecha_Derecha.svg"
        alt="Flecha Derecha"
        class="object-contain mt-8
            col-span-2 col-start-7 place-self-center
            sm:w-[165px]
            sm:col-span-2 sm:col-start-7 sm:place-self-center"
      />
      <div
        class="col-start-9 col-span-4 lg:col-start-9 lg:col-span-4 sm:col-start-10 sm:col-span-3 m-auto"
      >
        <RevealButton word={"Diferentes"} client:load />
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col items-center mt-8 sm:mt-24
            col-span-3 col-start-1"
      >
        <p class="text-[#6610F2] text-2xl sm:text-5xl text-extrabold">Hi</p>
        <AudioPlayer
          audio_path={"/audio/landing/Hi.mp3"}
          className="w-24 h-24 sm:w-20 sm:h-20"
          client:load
        />
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col items-center mt-8 sm:mt-24
            col-span-3 col-start-4"
      >
        <p class="text-[#6610F2] text-2xl sm:text-5xl text-extrabold">High</p>
        <AudioPlayer
          audio_path={"/audio/landing/High.mp3"}
          className="w-24 h-24 sm:w-20 sm:h-20"
          client:load
        />
      </div>
      <img
        src="/images/svg/landing/Flecha_Derecha.svg"
        alt="Flecha Derecha"
        class="object-contain mt-8
            col-span-2 col-start-7 place-self-center
            sm:w-[165px]
            sm:col-span-2 sm:col-start-7 sm:place-self-center"
      />
      <div
        class="col-start-9 col-span-4 lg:col-start-9 lg:col-span-4 sm:col-start-10 sm:col-span-3 m-auto"
      >
        <RevealButton word={"Diferentes"} client:load />
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col items-center mt-8 sm:mt-24
            col-span-3 col-start-1"
      >
        <p class="text-[#6610F2] text-2xl sm:text-5xl text-extrabold">Boat</p>
        <AudioPlayer
          audio_path={"/audio/landing/Boat.mp3"}
          className="w-24 h-24 sm:w-20 sm:h-20"
          client:load
        />
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col items-center mt-8 sm:mt-24
            col-span-3 col-start-4"
      >
        <p class="text-[#6610F2] text-2xl sm:text-5xl text-extrabold">Vote</p>
        <AudioPlayer
          audio_path={"/audio/landing/Vote.mp3"}
          className="w-24 h-24 sm:w-20 sm:h-20"
          client:load
        />
      </div>
      <img
        src="/images/svg/landing/Flecha_Derecha.svg"
        alt="Flecha Derecha"
        class="object-contain mt-8
            col-span-2 col-start-7 place-self-center
            sm:w-[165px]
            sm:col-span-2 sm:col-start-7 sm:place-self-center"
      />
      <div
        class="col-start-9 col-span-4 lg:col-start-9 lg:col-span-4 sm:col-start-10 sm:col-span-3 m-auto"
      >
        <RevealButton word={"Iguales"} client:load />
      </div>
    </section>
    <!-- Sección de "Tal como puedes notar" -->
    <section
      class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-[15px] w-[75%] sm:w-[75%] space-y-8 mx-auto mt-24"
    >
      <p
        class="text-base
            col-span-9 place-content-center
            sm:text-2xl"
      >
        Tal como puedes haber notado, la forma en que <span class="text-bold"
          >están escritas las palabras</span
        > y <span class="text-bold">cómo las leemos</span> son <span
          class="text-[#6610F2] text-bold">dos cosas distintas</span
        >. Por ejemplo, <span class="text-[#6610F2] text-bold">fur</span> y <span
          class="text-[#6610F2] text-bold">fir</span
        > se <span class="text-bold"
          >escriben distinto, pero se pronuncian igual</span
        >.
      </p>
      <img
        src="/images/svg/landing/Emoji_Bombilla.svg"
        alt="Emoji bombilla"
        class="col-span-3 my-auto"
      />
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>
